then that cytoplasmic flows and MT\nconformations can be used to differentiate between mechanisms and to determine\ntheir contribution to the migration process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2015 17:20:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-10"}
