rons in the\nsub-picosecond domain, which exerts on the metal lattices along with the\nnon-equilibrium heat flow. Our work that employs the parabolic two-step heating\nmodel to study the effect of the hot-electron blast in multi-layered thin metal\nfilms is also presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2015 16:42:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-12"}
